                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17800628-127-off629 t17800628-127-cd630"></join>, about the hour of ten in the night, and stealing thirteen yards of black silk lace, value 30 s. the property of the said William
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17800628-127-person1669">
                  WILLIAM
                   JONES
               <interp inst="t17800628-127-person1669" type="surname" value="JONES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17800628-127-person1669" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
